{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/Story.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br>In The Sun Shines Over Us, a narrative driven visual novel,you play as Mentari, a victim of bullying who just transferred schools and is trying to recover from her traumatic past. Help her make choices through her school life and experience life-changing events that will affect her future.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/Relationships.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br>In school, there are many unique students, each with their own different characters and neuroses. There are three main characters and each different platonic route depends on your choices throughout the story.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/Mental_Health.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br>Playing as Mentari, you will be facing different characters with a different understanding and challenges of mental health. Through the game, you will discover other characters\u2019 problems and you can also help each other through these perilous times!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/No_Game_Over.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br>You can always replay the game and discover new scenes you previously missed - what you missed the first time, you might find the second time! Choosing different options will open the different scenes and unlock deeper conversations with different characters.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/Anyone.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br>As the game isn\u2019t about twitch skills, it explores stories based on learning and empathy. Let your emotions take over in this strong narrative with unique characters each with their own perspective<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539620/extras/Game_Features.png?t=1732530577\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Story with <strong>15 chapters</strong>, spanning over <strong>100.000-word count</strong><br></li><li> <strong>6 different endings</strong> (no sad ending!)<br></li><li> <strong>15 Animated characters</strong> with 2 fashion styles<br></li><li> <strong>Over 25 beautifully rendered backgrounds</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Memorable BGM</strong><br></li><li> <strong>31 beautiful CG</strong> to collect across the game</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Starting Point","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/6c1e4a2f767d176dc78aa0a85e0e30e1349ea33a.jpg"},{"name":"One Step at a Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/98b2843925310b46979fad17e084d8452ee9d4fe.jpg"},{"name":"Resolution","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/0bae89065f4cd20316904be64b7bc0d412d12c0f.jpg"},{"name":"First Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/9ac9ea139d99b10a00f85df37a415d13d0e3b991.jpg"},{"name":"Sweet Candy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/142d4d0aa02a13dddd16dfdb16e656ad31dd36f5.jpg"},{"name":"New Friends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/591b52d05ef8bd4fd6ef640d0e9c722ab3ece840.jpg"},{"name":"Fuzzy Feeling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/fbe6482c139412f041db7a1e85b3daa2e36325e8.jpg"},{"name":"Student Council","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2539620/003d1d3160cc2e9265823dfee320bcc9e6de8f1d.jpg"},{"name":"Flower of Strength","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/